==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overget
<hw>O`ver*get"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
reach; to overtake; to pass.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To get beyond; to get over or recover from.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overgild</ent>⟦br⟧
